    "Each model was trained on one A100 GPU with 1000 epochs and the last checkpoint was used as the final model.",
    "The DeepLabV3+ specialist models used ResNet50 38 as the encoder.",
    "Similar to ref.",
    "3, the input images were resized to 224 × 224 × 3.",
    "The bounding box was transformed into a binary mask as an additional input channel to provide the object location prompt."
